room_title: Escape room "Diagonal Alley" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description:
A dark wizard grows in power – it is up to you and your fellow wizards and witches to stop them, and you’re running out of time!

Can you find and cleanse the six Crorhuxes of their dark magic? I hope so, or the whole wizarding world may be doomed…
